SummaryOfDirectChrtblActyGrp.Description1Txt: The Elsie & William Viles Foundation owns and maintains property located on Stone Street in Augusta, Maine that is available for use by not for profit organizations at no
SummaryOfDirectChrtblActyGrp.Description2Txt: charge. Organizations whose mission includes conservation, education, animal protection/welfare, and/or promote and preserve Maine history and culture are given priority in
SummaryOfDirectChrtblActyGrp.Description3Txt: scheduling the space. Activities and programs include seminars, meetings, retreats, workshops, symposia, and fundraising events.
